<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="zh-Hant">

<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>
        {% block title %}
        職能發展學院
        {% endblock %}
    </title>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="{{url_for('static',filename='css/base.css')}}">
</head>

<body>

    <header>
        <div class="navbar">
            <div class="navbar-left">
                <a href="#" class="logo">職能發展學院</a>
            </div>
            <div class="navbar-right">
                <ul class="nav-links">
                    <li><a href="{{url_for('index')}}">主頁</a></li>
                    <li><a href="{{url_for('classes')}}">課程規劃</a></li>
                    <li><a href="{{url_for('news')}}">最新訊息</a></li>
                    <li><a href="{{url_for('traffic')}}">交通資訊</a></li>
                    <li><a href="{{url_for('contact')}}">聯絡我們</a></li>
                </ul>
                <button class="menu-button">Menu</button>
            </div>
        </div>
    </header>

    <main>
        <section class="content">
            {% block main %}
            <h1>歡迎來到職能發展學院</h1>
            <p>這裡是網頁的主要內容區域。您可以放置任何您需要的資訊在這裡。</p>
            {% endblock %}
        </section>
    </main>

    <footer>
        <div class="footer-container">
            <div class="footer-logo">
                <img src="{{url_for('static',filename='images/justhome_logo.png')}}" alt="JustHome Logo">
            </div>
            <nav class="footer-nav">
                <a href="#">Discover</a>
                <a href="#">Quick Link</a>
                <a href="#">Contact Us</a>
                <a href="#">Our Address</a>
                <a href="#">Get App</a>
            </nav>
        </div>
        <div class="footer-copyright"> <span>&copy; 2025 職能發展學院 版權所有</span> </div>
    </footer>


    <script src="{{url_for('static',filename='js/testindex.js')}}"></script>

</body>

</html>